{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_01_01",
  "title": "星々が奇跡と叶える約束の未来 1話 スペシャルライブ作戦会議",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃあ、作戦会議を始めましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's start the strategy meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、琴乃ちゃん、報告してくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ Kotono-chan‚ could you give us your reports?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央さんにお願いして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked Rio-san to do it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワも計画に参加してくれることになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and LizNoir will also participate in the plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの三人も喜んで協力するって言ってくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three from TRINITYAiLE also said they'd be happy to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6355099678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "スリクスも事情を話したら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I explained the situation to IIIX‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1355099678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "特別に歌ってもいいと言ってくれたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they reluctantly agreed to sing as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3416289132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、渋々って感じだったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it seemed more like they did it unwillingly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2688433011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "これで星見プロのアイドル全員参加決定だね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ all the idols from Hoshimi Prods. will participate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6355099678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お世話になってる人達に日頃の感謝を伝えるって話が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems that the idea of expressing gratitude to those",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0688433011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "随分大事になりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "who have been taking care of us has become quite important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5534147035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "感謝の気持ちを表すために、スペシャルライブを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who was it that first suggested we should hold a special live concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0943532308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "やろうって最初に言い出したのは誰だったっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to express our gratitude?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2457025369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニピと月ストのみんなで話してたら、アイドルらしく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest were talking‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9825640996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "歌で感謝を伝えたいって話になったのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it naturally came up that we wanted to convey our gratitude through song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0017353701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "誰がというより、自然にみんながそうしたいと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than who suggested it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5492307663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "思ったんじゃないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think everyone just naturally felt that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつもお世話になってる三枝さん、さとみさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To Saegusa-san and Satomi-san‚ who always take care of us‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8825640996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それに{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and also to {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3492307663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなに感謝を伝えるスペシャルライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make the special live concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.349229749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "絶対成功させようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to express our gratitude a success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2929176648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "問題は会場と音響スタッフさんをどうするかだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problem is‚ what should we do about the venue and the sound staff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4158964157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけで全部手配出来るかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we arrange everything ourselves?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういうのはいつも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've always",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1762591362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに任せてたからね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "left that kind of thing to {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9762591362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのことなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8095924695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "会場の準備は私に任せてもらえないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "could I be in charge of preparing the venue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実は何年か前に、事務所に内緒でライブをやりたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ a few years ago‚ I secretly wanted to hold a live‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3095924695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "会場を借りようとしたことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I tried to rent the venue without the agency's knowledge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0762591362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "結局ライブは実現しなかったけど……あそこなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live concert never happened in the end‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8429258029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "事情を話せばステージを使わせてくれると思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "if I explain the situation‚ I think they'll let us use the stage there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1095924695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7762591362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そちらの手配は遙子さんにお任せします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll leave the arrangements to you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それからセトリなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ about the setlist…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4517691612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "各グループのセンター五人で歌ってほしい曲があるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want the centers out of each five groups to sing a particular song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7184358279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "五人で歌ってほしいって、どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sing with the center five people? What does that mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0851024945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
